---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import EligibilityChecker from '../components/EligibilityChecker.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Section 75 Claim Helper"
  description="Find out whether you have a valid Section 75 claim against your credit card provider, and what to do next. Free eligibility checker, full guide, and a £6.99 claim pack."
>
  <div class="space-y-12">

    <section>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">UK Consumer Credit Act 1974 — Section 75</p>
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
        Paid by credit card and something went wrong?
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        You may be able to claim your money back from your card provider — even if you only paid £1 on the card. Use our free checker to see whether Section 75 applies to your situation.
      </p>
      <a href="/#checker" class="btn-primary">Check eligibility — free</a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-gray-400">Under Section 75 of the Consumer Credit Act 1974, your card provider is jointly liable with the retailer.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <EligibilityChecker />
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What to do next</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="/guide/" class="block rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style="color: #1e3a5f;">Step 1</p>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Read the guide</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">How Section 75 works, who qualifies, and how to claim step by step.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/guide/section-75-vs-chargeback/" class="block rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style="color: #1e3a5f;">Step 2</p>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Section 75 or chargeback?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Which route applies to your situation, and how to tell the difference.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/claim-pack/" class="block rounded-lg border p-4 transition-colors hover:opacity-90" style="background-color: #1e3a5f; border-color: #1e3a5f;">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-white/60 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Step 3</p>
          <h3 class="font-medium text-white mb-1">Write your claim — £6.99</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Template letters, evidence checklists, and rejection rebuttals in one PDF.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="situations">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Browse by situation</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">Not sure where to start? Find your situation below — each page covers the specific evidence to gather, what your bank is likely to say, and how to respond.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {[
          { href: '/category/section-75-holiday-booking/',   label: 'Holiday booking',      desc: 'Travel company collapsed or cancelled without refunding' },
          { href: '/category/section-75-wedding-deposit/',   label: 'Wedding deposit',       desc: 'Venue, caterer, photographer, or other supplier failed' },
          { href: '/category/section-75-kitchen-deposit/',   label: 'Kitchen installation',  desc: 'Company went bust or failed to complete the fit' },
          { href: '/category/section-75-car-deposit/',       label: 'Car deposit',           desc: 'Dealer collapsed before delivery or car was misrepresented' },
          { href: '/category/section-75-furniture-deposit/', label: 'Furniture order',       desc: 'Retailer went into administration or goods not delivered' },
          { href: '/category/section-75-gym-membership/',    label: 'Gym membership',        desc: 'Gym closed mid-membership or upfront fee unused' },
          { href: '/category/section-75-building-work/',     label: 'Building work',         desc: 'Builder abandoned the job or work is seriously defective' },
        ].map(({ href, label, desc }) => (
          <a href={href} class="flex flex-col rounded-lg border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 hover:border-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">{label}</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">{desc}</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Find your bank</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">Each page covers how to contact the right team, what evidence to include, and how to respond to common rejection reasons specific to that bank.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        {[
          { href: '/guide/barclays-section-75/',  label: 'Barclaycard' },
          { href: '/guide/lloyds-section-75/',    label: 'Lloyds Bank' },
          { href: '/guide/halifax-section-75/',   label: 'Halifax' },
          { href: '/guide/hsbc-section-75/',      label: 'HSBC' },
          { href: '/guide/natwest-section-75/',   label: 'NatWest' },
          { href: '/guide/santander-section-75/', label: 'Santander' },
        ].map(({ href, label }) => (
          <a href={href} class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 hover:border-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 text-sm">{label}</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Section 75 guide ›</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Recent business failures</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">When a UK retailer or service provider goes into administration, we publish a specific Section 75 guide within 48 hours explaining what customers can claim and how. There are no new entries at present — <a href="/guide/" class="underline hover:text-gray-800">read the complete guide</a> for the full process.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5 text-sm text-gray-600">
      <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">What we do and do not do</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">We do</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1 list-disc list-inside marker:text-gray-400">
            <li>explain Section 75 in plain English;</li>
            <li>provide template letters and checklists;</li>
            <li>help you understand the process.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">We do not</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1 list-disc list-inside marker:text-gray-400">
            <li>handle your claim for you;</li>
            <li>contact your bank;</li>
            <li>take a percentage of your refund;</li>
            <li>give legal advice.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400"><a href="/disclaimer/" class="underline hover:text-gray-600">Full disclaimer</a></p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
